name: Suspicious Lakkaberry Pie
desc: A sweet treat from the borderlands. After mustering your full strength to bite through the near-impregnable crust, the coarse chunks of pastry grate against the inside of your mouth like rocks. Fortunately, just as you're questioning your life choices — or at least those that apply to baked goods — a slight hint of berries hits your palate, reminding you that you are, in fact, not eating frozen soil...
